These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  analyst, firefighter, nurse, pilot, security-guard, social-worker
There 6 different types of food: grapefruit, peas, potato, peach, garlic, raspberry
1. the pilot is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the person eating peas is on the left of the social-worker##1
3. the analyst is on the left of the firefighter##1
4. the person eating garlic is between the social-worker and the person eating grapefruit##2
5. the person eating peach is between the person eating garlic and the person eating peas##2
6. the person eating grapefruit is the pilot##1
7. the security-guard is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
8. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the firefighter##1
9. the security-guard is on the right of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Job           | analyst | firefighter | social-worker | security-guard | pilot    | nurse  |
| Food   | raspberry | peas   | peach       | garlic        | grapefruit | potato |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, fanta, milk, iced-tea
6 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig, horse, lizard, snake
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | iced-tea | milk | fanta | sprite | juice  |
| Pet           | snake | lizard  | frog | goat    | horse  | guinea-pig |

