.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
6 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, frog, guinea-pig, rabbit, snake
There are 6 different nationalities: indian, australian, french, american, russian, turkish
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the indian##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the russian##1
3. the indian is on the left of the american##1
4. the indian is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the indian##2
7. the australian is on the far left##1
8. the french is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Pet         | chinchilla | bird | snake      | rabbit | guinea-pig | frog      |
| Nationality   | australian    | turkish  | indian | american   | russian       | french |

