2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who growsorchid is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growslily##2
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
8. the person who growslily is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Flower   | zinnia   | bellflower    | rose | aconite | orchid | lily   |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | badminton | cycling | soccer | golf  | biathlon |

