.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, coffee, milk, 7up, mirinda
The people have 6 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing, reading, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
9. the person drinking cola is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Beverage    | cola | mirinda | 7up  | milk      | coffee | almond-milk  |
| Hobby   | card-games  | dancing    | reading | board-games | traveling | woodworking |

