.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-7::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, cooking, gardening, hiking, reading, skydiving
There 6 different types of food: raspberry, garlic, kale, avocado, watermelon, onion
1. the person eating avocado is the person eating avocado##1
2. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person eating onion##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person eating avocado and the person eating watermelon##2
7. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
9. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Hobby       | skydiving | hiking | chess | reading | gardening | cooking |
| Food   | kale | onion    | watermelon  | raspberry    | avocado    | garlic    |

