1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of trance is between the fan of jazz and the fan of blues##2
4. the dutch is the fan of gospel##1
5. the russian is between the japanese and the mexican##2
6. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of trance##1
7. the mexican is on the right of the turkish##1
8. the mexican is on the right of the turkish##1
9. the russian is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Nationality           | dutch | turkish | mexican | russian | japanese | spanish |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | indie   | disco         | blues    | trance     | jazz     |

