There are 6 different favourite colors: turquise, grey, white, red, blue, brown
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who likes red##1
 2. the person who likes turquise is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who likes brown##2
 3. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1
 4. the person who likes red is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 6. the person who likes red is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Hobby   | chess   | singing  | filmmaking | hiking | sudoku | gardening     |
| Color   | grey | turquise | brown    | blue | red | white |

