.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  bartender, nurse, software-developer, teacher, videographer, writer
6 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, scrabble, snooker, canasta, whist
 1. the software-developer is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 2. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the nurse is the person playing snooker##1
 4. the software-developer is between the teacher and the person playing whist##2
 5. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing whist and the videographer##2
 6. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the bartender##1
 7. the nurse is on the far left##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the bartender##1
 9. the person playing whist is the bartender##1
10. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Job           | nurse      | teacher | software-developer | bartender   | writer  | videographer |
| Game   | snooker | backgammon  | monopoly             | whist | scrabble | canasta       |

